    - "calendar_set": Set or add an event/reminder to the calendar (including recurring events like birthdays). E.g., "repeat birthday" should be classified as "calendar_set" because it refers to setting or scheduling a recurring calendar event.
    - "calendar_query": Look up or retrieve calendar information or upcoming events.
    - "alarm_set": Set or schedule an alarm.
    - "alarm_query": Look up existing alarms (what alarms are set, when, etc.).
